('위대한 쇼', 'The Great Show', '2019-08-26', '/wjpQc5Dy3p6RNhLICRNJXKnG0SM.jpg', 'ko', '/5AZ3KSfmM9gXR5HiwqJo9OQTX99.jpg', 'Wie Dae-Han  is an ex-lawmaker and is a materialistic kind of politician. He wants to get elected as lawmaker again. One day, 18-year-old girl Da-Jung comes to him. She tells him that he is her real father. Her mother raised four children, including Da-Jung, alone, but she died in a hit-and-run accident. Da-Jung is the only one now taking care of her 3 younger siblings. Wie Dae-Han accepts Da-Jung and her 3 younger siblings. He carries out “The Great Show” to become a lawmaker again.', 18, 4.082, 8.5, 'KR', 2, 92453),
('유령을 잡아라', 'Catch The Ghost', '2019-10-21', '/jaFm3oeh2UgvSBTXcEjWauOFHBg.jpg', 'ko', '/zlyM7pjbFP9tI69zd02Un2g2EMf.jpg', 'A romantic investigative drama about rookie detective Yoo-Ryung who solves cases with her overflowing sense of justice and exceptional spatial perception but always gets herself into trouble because of her rash actions. She meets the Wangsimni station constabulary chief, a man who avoids cases and seeks stability who always ends up cleaning up after the problems caused by Yoo Ryung and holds the key to solving the cases.', 35, 7.553, 7.5, 'KR', 2, 94615),
('유희열의 스케치북', 'You Hee-yeol\'s Sketchbook', '2009-04-24', '/gWTJDV0iRWkkiwlL5uXHQvRPbkk.jpg', 'ko', '/5zsoaVX483aJG90rJhlAup1VAXI.jpg', 'You Hee-yeol\'s Sketchbook is a Korean pop music program that is both a talk show and live music show. The host of this program is You Hee-yeol, also known as Toy, a one-man project band. This program has aired since April 24, 2009.', 10767, 8.869, 9, 'KR', 3, 39429),
('육룡이 나르샤', 'Six Flying Dragons', '2015-10-05', '/chPjgF2oT9wmxqaQPDwNpaSB6bK.jpg', 'ko', '/jRYtNDG4YrYPNyFDWqeaCh9fNgh.jpg', 'The ambitious success stories of 6 people surrounding Prince Lee Bang Won, and the ideological and political conflict between Prince Lee Bang Won and Jung Do Jeon, the man instrumental in helping King Taejo establish the fledgling Joseon nation.', 18, 4.922, 7.6, 'KR', 10, 63927),
('으라차차 와이키키', 'Welcome to Waikiki', '2018-02-05', '/w149cSXhmfSOWMeXgQi4HZ8doG8.jpg', 'ko', '/pggzZamoLNTiRgoYz8WVCISMCqv.jpg', 'Kang Dong-Goo dreams of becoming a movie director, but he is cynical due to bad luck. Cheon Joon-Ki wanted to follow in his father\'s footsteps and become an actor, but he is now just a minor actor. Bong-Doo-Sik came to Seoul to become a scenario writer, but things have not been easy for him.\n\nThese 3 men run the guest house Waikiki in Itaewon, South Korea. Their guest house is facing bankruptcy and then a mysterious baby and single mother appear at Waikiki.', 35, 3.569, 8.1, 'KR', 13, 76557),
('응답하라 1988', 'Reply 1988', '2015-11-06', '/cP8pdA2MZSPvbtEh1N9RFoh4KPs.jpg', 'ko', '/iaSzsfeCNekf07qBmPxJkbQ8zcU.jpg', 'There are five families living in the same neighbourhood of Ssangmundong, Dobong District, Northern Seoul. The neighbourhood is filled with warmth and love because everyone shares and cares for each other. Being the second daughter in the family with an elder sister and a younger brother, Sung Deok Sun often feels that she is being neglected by her parents. She finds out later that family is her only source of support when she is being harmed.', 35, 4.182, 7.9, 'KR', 24, 64010),
('응답하라 1994', 'Reply 1994', '2013-10-18', '/emgo3lVEjSmJVNCJChChOsNKpx1.jpg', 'ko', '/zjTisd5oU5VaY5wxZxK3aGZY5q6.jpg', 'Generation Y, meet Generation X: on the heels of the success of Answer Me 1997, ‘90s nostalgia continues with a series set in 1994. Journey with a group of high schoolers as they discover the now legendary—then new—K-pop group Seo Taiji and the Boys, as well as the Korean Basketball League, \"new\" technology, and grungy fashion trends. Sometimes you’ve just got to look to your past in order to appreciate the present. Every generation is sure to find something to love in this field trip back into time! ', 35, 5.119, 8.4, 'KR', 13, 58761),
('이규연의 스포트라이트', 'Spotlight', '2015-05-31', '/7oxGstccY4yC6rPMC3if5I6tKDJ.jpg', 'ko', '/haQOJjawTihes6Zkg26dCYWDrQU.jpg', '', 10763, 1.074, 8, 'KR', 2, 90631),
('이몽', 'Different Dreams', '2019-05-04', '/thQPqo6i4KfIbzrDs2grO2ZSX3P.jpg', 'ko', '/mdytdVRRJPkBI1auoPbQnZOIN9v.jpg', 'During the Japanese colonial rule of Korea, a Korean surgeon who was raised by a Japanese family becomes a spy for the Korean government.', 10759, 5.035, 7, 'KR', 2, 88359),
('이번 생은 처음이라', 'Because This Is My First Life', '2017-10-09', '/gF5T9ElejDTmZGYmXlBUYsH21zC.jpg', 'ko', '/aVVmGHCDf32LhFQBXmTXl2APAPw.jpg', 'Nam Se-Hee is a single man in his early 30\'s. He has chosen to not marry. He owns his home, but he owes a lot on his mortgage. Yoon Ji-Ho is a single woman in her early 30\'s. She does not own a home and envies those that do. She has given up on dating due to her financial struggles. Yoon Ji-Ho begins to live at Nam Se-Hee’s house. They become housemates.', 35, 5.43, 8.6, 'KR', 23, 74074),
('이웃집 꽃미남', 'Flower Boy Next Door', '2013-01-07', '/glY4yjsRxL0fpz7ZgZlATP1L8UZ.jpg', 'ko', '/1Ne2iaZ74QhUXtZCE1ViC6vHAsK.jpg', 'Go Dok Mi doesn\'t spend all day dreaming about her knight in shining armor — she’s too busy spying on her neighbors who all happen to be hot, \"flower-boy\" types, including cartoon artist Oh Jin Rak. But when Enrique Geum, the new pretty boy next door, catches her, Dok Mi is finally forced to face the consequences - without the safety of binoculars and curtains. Will he be able to convince this “urban Rapunzel” to let her hair down? Whether you’re a lover or a fighter, this sensitive man will captivate your sensibilities.', 35, 4.533, 7.9, 'KR', 11, 46550),
('이태원 클라쓰', 'Itaewon Class', '2020-01-31', '/rtYQCa2NzX8RspbOmwfAla6BemO.jpg', 'ko', '/cIDpRmkTZnNib3ar7mhZBl7mGrO.jpg', 'On the first day of attending his new high school, Park Sae Roy gets into trouble after punching Jang Geun Won, who had been bullying a fellow classmate. Jang Dae Hee, the father of Jang Geun Won, is the CEO of the restaurant business Jagga, and the boss of Park Sae Roy father. After refusing to apologize for punching Jang Geun Won, Park Sae Roy father is fired, and he is ultimately expelled from school. Soon after, a tragic accident, caused by Jang Geun Won, takes place and Park Sae Ro Yoy’s father dies. Heartbroken and angry at his loss, Park Sae Roy viciously beats Jang Geun Won, earning himself time in prison. Deciding to take revenge upon the Jagga compony and the Jang family, Park Sae Roy opens his own restaurant in Itaewon, Seoul.', 0, 37.21, 5, 'KR', 2, 96162),
('자체발광 오피스', 'Radiant Office', '2017-03-15', '/2bxpm1qW5W4RjValqLwzLxONKWD.jpg', 'ko', '/5cpANNfhpYNfPxvUNmQyvtMVTkQ.jpg', 'Ho Won is a young woman who struggles to find a steady job. Tired and hopeless, she attempted suicide. Hospital check-up discovers she might have terminal illness. Soon after, a furniture company accepts her as a contract worker. Faced with a possibility of dying, Ho Won decides to just let herself loose. Her newfound bold attitude puts her at odds with her workaholic manager Woo Jin.', 35, 6.737, 7.4, 'KR', 6, 70195),
('장난스런 키스', 'Mischievous Kiss', '2010-11-02', '/fd3Ge0GjGr0phNISlDkUMkgDqVs.jpg', 'ko', '/mSjKpNVYGxOL17vcEbQ0nzYjOH2.jpg', 'Playful Kiss is a 2010 South Korean romantic-comedy television series, starring Jung So-min and Kim Hyun-joong. It aired on MBC from September 1 to October 21, 2010 on Wednesdays and Thursdays at 21:55 for 16 episodes.\n\nIt is based on the Japanese manga Itazura Na Kiss written by Tada Kaoru. The Korean series is the third television adaptation of the manga following the Taiwanese It Started With a Kiss in 2005, and its sequel They Kiss Again in 2007. Though Playful Kiss received low ratings in South Korea in the five to seven percent range, it was sold to 12 countries in Asia. Due to its international popularity, a short special edition was aired on YouTube after the series finale.\n\nThe story is about Oh Ha-ni, a clumsy student who falls for the perfectionist, Baek Seung-jo. However, Seung-jo is indifferent towards her and rejects her love. When Ha-ni\'s house collapses, she and her father moves into his long-time friend\'s house. It turns out that Seung-jo is the friend\'s son and Ha-ni is given the opportunity to be near the guy she loves. Will she be able to move Seung-jo\'s heart?', 35, 3.578, 7.3, 'KR', 13, 34408),
('저스티스', 'Justice', '2019-07-17', '/3GfvoKn1I4AxfMPWOigPgUT7EQY.jpg', 'ko', '/nuHSx0ANZ2Bmf3tpjEt3NUuP4gt.jpg', 'Lee Tae-Kyung is a star lawyer with the best win rate. He is able to win cases by using his sharp logic and intelligent speeches. Lee Tae-Kyung amasses power and wealth by dealing with clients who are part of the elite class.', 18, 4.004, 7, 'KR', 1, 91034),
('정글의 법칙', 'Law of the Jungle', '2011-10-21', '/7goeSggajsAa96CHG48vWrJz2o2.jpg', 'ko', '/qG2JpIDuYhuQOMSLqmMtHBBbfx5.jpg', 'Law of the Jungle is a hybrid reality show combining elements of drama and documentary. The show is hosted by comedian Kim Byung Man, and each episode invites various celebrities from the various field. So far, many of idol stars and famous actors have appeared on the show. The show introduces viewers to exotic locations around the world where celebrities must work together in order to complete missions and survive. The cast celebrities travel to less habituated, natural places to survive on their own and experience life with local tribes and people. In each location, the guests are tasked to hunt and prepare their meals and also create shelter for the tribe. They sometimes confronted by many difficult challenges. Where will the tribe visit? And how will they survive on their own? Stay tuned to check out!', 10764, 6.475, 0, 'KR', 0, 52910),
('제왕의 딸, 수백향', 'Su Baek-hyang, The King\'s Daughter', '2013-09-30', '/yVHLWrzRzGUB4lxXplMcN3D9tM8.jpg', 'ko', '/u4HwMwg8YIoh3DPWMPJH6ZnZUGL.jpg', 'This is the story of Su Baek-hyang, born as the elder daughter of King Mu-ryeong but unable to retain her title of princess due to her ambitious younger sister, Sol-hui. Humble and hard-working, she was taught never to want or to desire beyond what she has, but the fate given to her is one that will affect not only her life and her family\'s lives, but the entire nation as she struggles to find her place in life and fight for love.', 18, 1.844, 7, 'KR', 1, 61324),
('조선로코 - 녹두전', 'The Tale of Nokdu', '2019-09-30', '/wHHtlHWP0L2xps6ZsQuiLQTMa7B.jpg', 'ko', '/r8BhphHIruCL2jM4sd1Zs6sMJov.jpg', 'This romantic comedy drama set in the Joseon dynasty is about Jeon Nok-Du, a man who disguises as a woman to enter a mysterious women-only village, and Dong Dong-Ju, a young woman who does not want to become a gisaeng.', 35, 5.003, 9, 'KR', 3, 93541),
('조선생존기', 'Joseon Survival', '2019-06-08', '/gFJ09d3rLNK4iiAO634a0ZqO5A0.jpg', 'ko', '/7S9BBN3C5w3P09aD1G5lpCrKb8V.jpg', 'Han Jung-Rok is a former national archer and current deliveryman from 2019. He ends up traveling to the past with his first love, Lee Hye-Jin and meets Im Kkeok-Jeong, a famous thief from the Joseon dynasty. Together, they struggle to survive, put their lives at stake for the people they love, and share a strong friendship.', 10759, 4.013, 8.5, 'KR', 2, 90034),
('주간 아이돌', 'Weekly Idol', '2011-07-23', '/tb0w5OFohHZAv3h5GkT8ajYnanp.jpg', 'ko', '/vEZf0wQvQ4BQy9K9JpEKmrdgwIt.jpg', 'Weekly Idol is back with all new hosts. Cho Sae Ho, Hwang Kwang Hee and Nam Chang Hee are sticking together as a new unit group for Weekly Idol, a.k.a CKN Trio, to turn the idol world upside down! Get ready for their hot debut! Cho Sae Ho transforms himself into an idol expert. The hottest entertainer in the show business is marching into the idol world after taking over variety shows and he\'s more than ready to dominate the show with his amazing look and talents. They say idols understand each other best! As soon as being discharged from military service, Hwang Kwang Hee is reenlisted in Weekly Idol as a senior and a mentor to cheer his fellow idol friends. And lastly, the hidden card of the trio, Nam Chang Hee joins Weekly Idol. With his irresistible charms and talents, Nam Chang Hee becomes the irreplaceable member of Weekly Idol and shows off his amazing chemistry with idols.', 10767, 4.438, 8, 'KR', 1, 52823),
('주몽', 'Jumong', '2006-05-15', '/cUerXcchK9XmqbIBlCHCmVXaW34.jpg', 'ko', '/kRpA9uCTl3O6H7cPAnj4JcxrZlz.jpg', 'Jumong  examines the life of Jumong Taewang, founder of the kingdom of Goguryeo. Few details have been found in the historical record about Jumong, so much of the series is fictionalized. The fantastic elements surrounding the original Jumong legend have been replaced with events more grounded in reality.', 18, 11.457, 8.8, 'KR', 6, 4734),
('진짜 농구, 핸섬 타이거즈', 'Handsome Tigers', '2020-01-10', '/zMSuFPNVeJ3pjfA9DTpxy8rsufV.jpg', 'ko', '/zd1fEowG0a2ZAdeFfIpqAUycVso.jpg', 'The legendary basketball star Seo Jang Hoon is here as a head coach to revitalize the Korean basketball. He teamed up with various members with a passion for basketball and named it “Handsome Tigers.”', 10764, 3.488, 0, 'KR', 0, 97733),
('질투의 화신', 'Don\'t Dare to Dream', '2016-08-24', '/hoz1NCJR9RHROtPMvIdUov1LWRy.jpg', 'ko', '/1HbFVRZFWNcglKhY7caExczrCN6.jpg', 'Depicts the fierce competition at a broadcasting station and the love between anchor Lee Hwa-Shin and weather caster Pyo Na-Ri.', 35, 6.4, 7.8, 'KR', 13, 66560),
('집사부일체', 'Master In The House', '2017-12-31', '/cqgQR4ZRWbjz3emoYRnNPR3VISU.jpg', 'ko', '/unKeISg4CI2b94dhaQslHL2rCws.jpg', 'Almost everyone has a question regarding life and the goal of life. In order to find the answer, the four young men with full of curiosity regarding their lives, Lee Seung Gi, Lee Sang Yun, Yuk Seong Jae, and Yang Se Hyeong, head to find their master to learn things and get a correct answer. They find the master and spend a day in the master’s place to learn things that they didn’t know, and wish to know. Whom will they get to meet? And what will they learn throughout the stay?', 10764, 2.751, 10, 'KR', 1, 76033),
('청춘불패', 'Invincible Youth', '2009-10-23', '/dYySSFtAgdkCldjzxdwV7w1hKqh.jpg', 'en', '/hHGMZKkmBW35UkeUIBxxq7S1f2y.jpg', 'From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.\n\nInvincible Youth (Hangul: 청춘불패; hanja: 靑春不敗; RR: Cheongchun bulpae) is a South Korean variety show which aired its first season on KBS2 from October 23, 2009 to December 24, 2010. Season 1 featured seven girls (collectively known as G7) from K-pop idol groups wherein they experience how it is to live and survive in the Korean rural outdoors. It started its second season on November 12, 2011 featuring eight girls.', 35, 1.939, 0, 'KR', 0, 32391),
('청춘시대', 'Hello, My Twenties!', '2016-07-22', '/cRNfe3y7yUxVvUAjAKDJSoKUzxu.jpg', 'ko', '/qj3m22w9IjrXzZrVMHg8QLAQP3.jpg', 'University students Yoon Jin-Myung, Jung Ye-Eun, Song Ji-Won, Kang Yi-Na and Yoo Eun-Jae share a house. Jin-Myung is busy supporting herself financially and studying. She suffers from lack of sleep. Ye-Eun is devoted to her boyfriend, she is clear about what she likes or not. Ji-Won has a bright personality and likes to drink. Yi-Na is popular due to her beautiful appearance. Eun-Jae is timid, but she has an unique taste for men.', 35, 5.279, 6.1, 'KR', 32, 67014),
('초면에 사랑합니다', 'The Secret Life of My Secretary', '2019-05-06', '/xL102ZnaQNHqHapGo4Wk7RFOTsa.jpg', 'ko', '/7owGMGmnlx2EMEm3yFPQ03C0zjr.jpg', 'Do Min-Ik works as a director of the mobile media 1 team at T&T. He is smart and excellent at his job. His secretary is Jung Gal-Hee. Do Min-Ik often does childish things like calling Jung Gal-Hee continually. Jung Gal-Hee carries out Do Min-Ik\'s orders without complaints. She looks soft, but she hides her tough side.', 35, 5.945, 9, 'KR', 3, 88783),
('초콜릿', 'Chocolate', '2019-11-29', '/8hsrRG1Dw37I4yisvz7TxFUvx49.jpg', 'ko', '/lo9m03N7xfa56wYN58DlDdWcOjC.jpg', 'The story of a man who became a neurosurgeon though he dreamed of becoming a cook, and a woman who became a cook because of him.\n\nLee Kang is a neurosurgeon, who once dreamed of becoming a chef. As a child, Moon Cha Young once met Lee Kang at a small restaurant in the seaside town. There, Lee Kang cooked and gave her a meal, which in part inspired her to become a world-famous chef. Many years later, the two meet again at a hospice ward and together they heal their own emotional scars by preparing meals for the patients there.', 18, 3.773, 6, 'KR', 2, 95066),
('최고의 치킨', 'The Best Chicken', '2019-01-02', '/2i7trs7pLajB7uDPyzRqdFhCCty.jpg', 'ko', '/pXmONNKo2Dwx6Q5Yz1gA6ynXxSM.jpg', 'One day, Park Choi Go, decides to quit his job at a big company and open up his own chicken restaurant at what used to be a bathhouse. Meanwhile, Seo Bo Ah, an aspiring webtoon writer who secludes herself in the bathhouse, can’t accept that the building she inherited from her grandfather is turning into a chicken restaurant. To take her inheritance back, she becomes Park Choi Go’s employee along with Andrew Kang, a once promising chef who is now homeless. Can Park Choi Go become the ultimate chicken master and achieve his dream?', 35, 4.779, 0, 'KR', 0, 85415),
('출동 슈퍼윙스', 'Super Wings!', '2015-03-14', '/vwgC68MFTgrLaTBaXFnsVAb6y1W.jpg', 'ko', '/lu2DNsIQgn1Jb6djHvrqJSUQXXl.jpg', 'An action-packed preschool series about an adorable jet plane named Jett who travels the world delivering packages to children. On every delivery, Jett encounters a new problem that the he and his friends the Super Wings must work together to solve!', 16, 8.992, 7.3, 'KR', 3, 71026),
('치즈인더트랩', 'Cheese in the Trap', '2016-01-04', '/cI8J1ltg2JYfJ0YolCZHpRjPE7a.jpg', 'ko', '/6enInCnulRZqpZkddeTZFHadxx.jpg', 'Hong Seol and Yoo Jung attend the same college, but they couldn\'t be more different. Hong Seol is a poor, unpopular student with no money, while Yoo Jung is rich, well-liked, extremely smart, and popular. Hong Seol just wants to get through her college career quietly, but finds herself getting caught up in whatever Yoo Jung drags her into. Can Hong Seol break away, or will she continue to be the only person who sees Yoo Jung\'s true self?', 35, 6.309, 7.7, 'KR', 20, 64548),
('캐리어를 끄는 여자', 'Woman with a Suitcase', '2016-09-26', '/nS3gXQbdK9xfozh3Nxaq34ZaeSO.jpg', 'ko', '/fxJ9MDqooHAuLGpRdcWXiCZIuhC.jpg', 'A successful career woman gets framed for a crime and works her way back up after serving her time. She was once an office manager with a thriving career, but that takes a major hit when she is penalized for violating the Attorneys-at-Law Act and sent to prison for it. The drama follows the success story as she comes back as an ex-con, and follows her dream to become an outstanding lawyer.', 80, 3.023, 7.1, 'KR', 6, 67781),
('킬미, 힐미', 'Kill Me, Heal Me', '2015-01-07', '/17GaPSqkckU5ousG5UQ25hLNjtP.jpg', 'ko', '/dNH6NO0akHMIqbq5EC4qnCeeuC6.jpg', 'Cha Do Hyun is a rich heir to a family company with one major problem. Due to suppressed childhood trauma, he suffers from dissociative identity disorder manifested in 7 unique personalities who are out of his control. In order to overcome this disorder in secret, he hires a first year medical resident to help him heal by killing off each personality one by one.', 35, 4.541, 8.7, 'KR', 22, 62266),
('킹덤', 'Kingdom', '2019-01-25', '/aFmqXViWzIKmhR8Cy4QDqPU6pIL.jpg', 'ko', '/AsICtiVtz4icMQQRwDvOzfaTzjK.jpg', 'In this zombie thriller set in Korea\'s medieval Joseon dynasty, a crown prince is sent on a suicide mission to investigate a mysterious outbreak.', 18, 10.066, 8.3, 'KR', 74, 70593),
('태양의 계절', 'A Place in the Sun', '2019-06-03', '/AcvX1rYbWYtJQ0FTu1MxA15axM.jpg', 'ko', '/iCQTcnq1iVuz3HnVGLTVXvAirKy.jpg', 'When an orphan raised by foster parents has a near death experience, he changes his name and disappears from his life including his girlfriend. Attempting to cope, his girlfriend begins work at the conglomerate company Yangji Group where they meet again.', 18, 4.818, 8, 'KR', 1, 89765),
('태양의 후예', 'Descendants of the Sun', '2016-02-24', '/jDIzEfjoKA3Xhv8a7sXbu2C0Qp0.jpg', 'ko', '/5JECa3CZfgVQFabmiZKm1L3XSXj.jpg', 'A drama about the love of people who get closer as they learn to be considerate of each other in desperate times and sacrifices made by people who throw themselves into natural disasters.', 18, 8.032, 7.1, 'KR', 49, 65143);

