('Alexa & Katie', 'Alexa & Katie', '2018-03-23', '/puakB1M78oqHoyf6qP1Nfx9IMse.jpg', 'en', '/jVLqM6g5vF63Zq650lNSgtDx6hW.jpg', 'Lifelong best friends Alexa and Katie are eagerly anticipating the start of their freshman year of high school. The pals confront a crisis that leaves them feeling like outsiders at a time when what seems to matter most is fitting in.', 35, 6.81, 7.5, 'US', 19, 76874),
