('Bizaardvark', 'Bizaardvark', '2016-06-24', '/ie1aH3WvBOSHeZSI9o20xL6jqpy.jpg', 'en', '/r3zf9m6nvK55KhMukTqAg5rVEW7.jpg', 'The live-action comedy follows comedy duo Paige and Frankie, two quirky teens who write funny songs and create music comedy videos for their online channel. With the help of friend and aspiring agent Bernie plus Vuuugle stars Dirk and Amelia, the best friends embark on comedic adventures in their quest to take the video blogging world by storm.', 35, 7.238, 6.3, 'US', 25, 66456),
