('Der letzte Bulle', 'The Last Cop', '2010-04-12', '/xEbm6Uwgz3QlpdCNbkr9FBVnzw8.jpg', 'de', '/6cjsCEh3jAuncgNh6pQKjHJYYj6.jpg', 'Der letzte Bulle is a German television series that was first aired in 2010. The series is about a cop from the 1980s put into a modern police department in Essen.', 35, 3.346, 6.7, 'DE', 3, 41064),
('Der Pass', 'Pagan Peak', '2019-01-25', '/61HHanDa9nIqqwezeuXWfWM4y7d.jpg', 'de', '/oTlfrDYSVgVGE0zw1fmPguhe7Ih.jpg', 'When a gruesomely staged body is found, propped up on a mountain pass in the Alps close to the German-Austrian border, two detectives are sent to investigate. For German detective Ellie, this is the first real challenge of her career; her Austrian counterpart Gedeon though seems to have lost any ambitions in his job. Very soon, they discover more crime scenes with symbolically posed victims, reminiscent of pagan rituals. It all seems to be part of a bigger, sinister plan. Ellie finds herself under increasing pressure to understand the deranged killer\'s motives so she can stop him. The hunt leads them ever deeper in the dark valleys and archaic Alpine customs - and the paranoid world of the killer.', 10759, 8.171, 7.4, 'DE', 17, 85526),
('Der Staatsanwalt hat das Wort', 'Der Staatsanwalt hat das Wort', '1965-10-21', '/v9Trr5OaLcfwXe22tOiFqVileaG.jpg', 'de', '/tjivLHat0lu0buLeXWUu9kApsid.jpg', 'Der Staatsanwalt hat das Wort was an East German television series.', 80, 2.467, 0, 'DE', 0, 40938),
('Der Tatortreiniger', 'Crime Scene Cleaner', '2011-12-23', '/8FyewquYtwkFbXPoD3JgbNpj4ye.jpg', 'de', '/2eYY081ucLbaqTOfiQRYsG7UP4a.jpg', 'Heiko Schotte (Schotty) works for a cleaning company, cleaning all kind of crime scenes. There he sometimes meets weird people and tries to solve difficult situations.', 35, 5.961, 7.9, 'DE', 51, 51488),
('Derek', 'Derek', '2013-01-30', '/cWK9WMZ2EY5FpNQdGZamsqkEAaK.jpg', 'en', '/pfwyBM2bi20EFUg6bQural5YhcL.jpg', 'Derek is a loyal nursing home caretaker who sees only the good in his quirky co-workers as they struggle against prejudice and shrinking budgets to care for their elderly residents.', 35, 3.758, 7.2, 'GB', 66, 60655),
('Derrick', 'Derrick', '1974-10-20', '/a2NRob5tRPgWxkbY2xYXypZ5n8F.jpg', 'de', '/begCtQZl9cSK8mdtJT4IwPzyAMF.jpg', 'Derrick was a German TV series produced by Telenova Film und Fernsehproduktion in association with ZDF, ORF and SRG between 1974 and 1998 about Detective Chief Inspector Stephan Derrick and his loyal assistant Inspector Harry Klein, who solve murder cases in Munich and surroundings.', 80, 17.797, 5.1, 'DE', 8, 4583),
('Derry Girls', 'Derry Girls', '2018-01-04', '/aF9sIUIXyIagWy7OftzkgRZ6310.jpg', 'en', '/itBpxZib594NbwqTU2lm4rO8tIY.jpg', 'Amidst the political conflict of Northern Ireland in the 1990s, five high school students square off with the universal challenges of being a teenager.', 35, 5.372, 8.2, 'GB', 27, 76148),
