('Just Add Magic: Mystery City', 'Just Add Magic: Mystery City', '2020-01-17', '/iuSBGQAW0SvVl8fXNefxK6LwCek.jpg', 'en', '/qyxOHsLpn6ktH9gFngCV3AHvG9c.jpg', 'In a spinoff of the successful series Just Add Magic, we follow the magic cookbook to Bay City as it moves to three new protectors: step-siblings Zoe and Leo, and their downstairs neighbor Ish. Each of the three brings a unique skill to the table, as the cookbook unlocks a centuries-old mystery that takes them on an historical adventure through the city streets in a race to find a secret recipe.', 16, 4.322, 8, 'US', 1, 98078),
