('Justified', 'Justified', '2010-03-16', '/chYA7LQVESXOHdtE0ocGm6344TM.jpg', 'en', '/pv3OcewyqMpnIZUOSTxiFnSJaki.jpg', 'A character drama based on the 2001 Elmore Leonard short story \"Fire in the Hole.\" Leonard\'s tale centers around U.S. Marshal Raylan Givens of Kentucky, a quiet but strong-willed official of the law. The tale covers his high-stakes job, as well as his strained relationships with his ex-wife and father.', 80, 15.418, 8, 'US', 320, 1436),
('K-Project', 'K-Project', '2012-10-05', '/v1CRWKQd0pfPbpsTx1m8ca4AvLi.jpg', 'ja', '/52eQfCm8yGEQHNZefyHr6uIysqt.jpg', 'Shiro is an easygoing teenager content with just being a student—until his seemingly perfect life is halted when a bloodthirsty clan, glowing red with fire, attempts to kill him in the streets. Unbeknownst to Shiro, he is suspected of murdering a member of their clan and will need a miracle to escape their vengeance. Miraculously, a young man named Kurou Yatogami swings in and aids Shiro in his getaway, only to reveal he\'s also after Shiro\'s life. Now a hunted man, Shiro will have to evade the clans of seven powerful kings and desperately try to prove his innocence—before it’s too late!', 16, 8.586, 6.6, 'JP', 18, 45799),
('K.C. Undercover', 'K.C. Undercover', '2015-01-18', '/31GZblRVe1DPZXbxTL5aVWTPJ9f.jpg', 'en', '/1tq8ao1v28f6DpNfUVMKyiruBwl.jpg', 'K.C. Cooper, a high school math whiz and karate black-belt, learns that her parents are spies when they recruit her to join them in the secret government agency, The Organization. While she now has the latest spy gadgets at her disposal, K.C. has a lot to learn about being a spy, including keeping her new gig a secret from her best friend Marisa. Together, K.C. and her parents, Craig and Kira, and her younger siblings, Ernie and Judy (a humanoid robot), try to balance everyday family life while on undercover missions, near and far, to save the world.', 35, 8.851, 7, 'US', 48, 61915),
('Kaamelott', 'Kaamelott', '2005-01-03', '/hFKxXCrFnF6sLfI9l0GBT944wWF.jpg', 'fr', '/d6P4O0LzE4WFp4GnSkzauUTmC2P.jpg', 'In this off beat account of King Arthur\'s quest for the Grail, virtually every journey, battle or adventure is stopped dead in its tracks by the knights of the round table\'s most worldly traits : cowardice, greed, idiocy or misplaced chivalry. As a consequence, instead of epic adventures we are treated with the characters\' pragmatic and anachronistic take on each and every event in the Grail legend, true to the purest sitcom tradition.', 18, 10.363, 8.1, 'FR', 41, 11466),
('Kaçak', 'Kaçak', '2013-09-24', '/m87DRZS2jctf7q96jgsWUOhw2KE.jpg', 'tr', '/n0OEMc1agvM5EnZy9EMqzzo08YY.jpg', 'The continuing life of an ex cop who had worked for a mafia undercover. Ended up killing the mafias son so later on he used the mafias daughter to escape. Falling in a unwanted love with her.', 10759, 5.217, 7, 'TR', 2, 63858),
('Kadın', 'Woman', '2017-10-24', '/v50t6JqLE7RC9sk7iwwkxhSsgQe.jpg', 'tr', '/6zfJPMwqsA5Roi5JCN7MZQRbykW.jpg', 'The story of mother Bahar, who carries the weight and love of two children in their hearts with enthusiasm in their hearts. Bahar, abandoned by her mother when she was eight years old, later lost her grandma and her father. When she thinks she is all alone, she meets Sarp, whom she delicately loves.', 18, 4.868, 9.7, 'TR', 3, 77532),
