('Koffee with Karan', 'Coffee with Karan', '2004-11-19', '/m3jYKxdsfyDVS0ZU16PsGEspo26.jpg', 'hi', '/yjJ2wEgeuisvNKzA5WpxCAiOBZf.jpg', 'Celebrity host Karan Johar gets up close and personal with various Bollywood personalities and discusses their major career milestones.', 10767, 7.838, 4.7, 'IO', 12, 14544),
