('Restaurant: Impossible', 'Restaurant: Impossible', '2011-01-19', '/hwpoeLVP2VsvVqZcOU8CMBHSuFf.jpg', 'en', '/q5lCbuk4obBqUtlx1969wSD0qNh.jpg', 'Chef Robert Irvine tries to turn around restaurants across America that are facing an impending demise if things don\'t improve. With a $10,000 budget and two days to work, Irvine uses his creativity and resourcefulness to turn the eatery\'s fortunes around.', 10764, 5.508, 6.2, 'US', 14, 35358),
