('Sam & Cat', 'Sam & Cat', '2013-06-08', '/xSdsvFqc2NaLbWvlT0fP2WEmFEy.jpg', 'en', '/gtHTWJWXDdnEGLoNYWTpez0cbkH.jpg', 'Sam & Cat is an American teen sitcom that premiered June 8, 2013, on Nickelodeon. It is a crossover spin-off/sequel of both iCarly and Victorious. It stars Jennette McCurdy as Sam Puckett and Ariana Grande as Cat Valentine. The girls meet by chance during a bizarre adventure and become roommates, then start a babysitting business to earn extra money.', 35, 6.843, 7.3, 'US', 46, 45666),
