('Samantha Who?', 'Samantha Who?', '2007-10-15', '/dR4vYaAcq1O7l3Z7GTjQCTMhRBg.jpg', 'en', '/6LtH15UL6jWA5TJxqDEKQZyrEvv.jpg', 'Samantha Newly has been a bad, bad girl. But thanks to an 8-day coma, she can\'t remember a thing. Fortunately her best friend Andrea is by her side with a cocktail and the 4-1-1 on every dirty deed. But the more Sam pieces together her past, the less she likes her old self. Maybe this is a chance to start over and do it all again.', 35, 7.273, 6.7, 'US', 29, 2739),
