('Santos Dumont', 'Santos Dumont', '2019-11-10', '/l3W9KjW2e0HzrbbVULqAb3OV2Pq.jpg', 'pt', '/3RteO9naJ8pTJMItZBpkB6NuNbT.jpg', 'The story of the man who embodied the great transformations of the turn of the century, acclaimed almost worldwide as the first man to fly a plane - the 14 Bis. Set in France and Brazil in the late 19th and early 20th centuries, the production follows the aviator\'s trajectory, from his childhood at his family\'s coffee plantations in the interior of Minas Gerais, to the sophisticated Paris lounges and air clubs.', 18, 4.922, 6, 'BR', 1, 94449),
('Sarabhai vs Sarabhai', 'Sarabhai vs Sarabhai', '2004-11-08', '/j22XVoD9XNuHRYCAi5tUbUL4UK2.jpg', 'hi', '/byesKCfOMingamle6FC4qDQ2ZsO.jpg', 'Sarabhai vs Sarabhai is a 2005 sitcom featuring a quintessentially upper-class family in Mumbai. The show received a positive response from the critics and public alike and enjoyed one of the best TRPs for an Indian comedy show. In the final episode, the principal characters are seen stating that there would be another season of the series. However, in 2012, Deven Bhojani denied that the series would return.', 35, 5.785, 5.2, 'IO', 21, 4165),
('Satisfaction', 'Satisfaction', '2014-07-17', '/pQPEkbsH5Dkec7YBURScJmduInN.jpg', 'en', '/vBR3pjNeRHzwhI0mZWJ9CUzTp95.jpg', 'A provocative drama that explores modern marriage at its midpoint. Through the lens of one couple, Neil Truman and his wife, Grace, this series answers the question, “What do you do when having it all is not enough?” by delving into their shocking and unconventional choices.', 18, 4.884, 5.8, 'US', 19, 61213),
