('Senke nad Balkanom', 'Shadows over Balkans', '2017-10-22', '/aAKpjDUWCkxJYCY1n2P0e5MsItU.jpg', 'sr', '/jmh0hWOAy0C68EpWDTSYlUh3JPk.jpg', 'A historical fiction drama and thriller set in the turbulent period of the late 1930s in the Balkans as a place where high politics, local interests, capital and crime all merge together.', 80, 5.601, 9.6, 'RS', 4, 74647),
