('Sense and Sensibility', 'Sense and Sensibility', '2008-01-01', '/kZXRChfXnj6fMHZazE8IBq1KIn5.jpg', 'en', '/2v0o81hCFoacfvDcXaisA2XldFU.jpg', 'Marianne Dashwood wears her heart on her sleeve when she falls in love with the charming but unsuitable John Willoughby, ignoring her sister Elinor\'s warning that her impulsive behavior leaves her open to gossip and innuendo. Elinor, sensitive to social convention, struggles to conceal her own romantic disappointment, even from those closest to her. Will the sisters learn that sense must mix with sensibility if they are to find personal happiness in a society where status and money govern the rules of love?', 18, 5.164, 7.7, 'GB', 56, 13892),
('Sense8', 'Sense8', '2015-06-05', '/o9lkuOw0UijHi6o1VRVVCT3Ivul.jpg', 'en', '/kmyvlQ9QKzgdZY31rXaUlgCnzrB.jpg', 'One gunshot, one death, one moment out of time that irrevocably links eight minds in disparate parts of the world, putting them in each other\'s lives, each other\'s secrets, and in terrible danger. Ordinary people suddenly reborn as \"Sensates.\"', 18, 18.673, 7.7, 'US', 578, 61664),
('Servant', 'Servant', '2019-11-28', '/digxxEISFHSPOLpBFbZnQqm9nhD.jpg', 'en', '/n5iDow3TLI74e0W41363ieKucei.jpg', 'A Philadelphia couple are in mourning after an unspeakable tragedy creates a rift in their marriage and opens the door for a mysterious force to enter their home.', 18, 20.24, 8.1, 'US', 41, 88055),
('Sesame Street', 'Sesame Street', '1969-11-10', '/zIbkxRfoDXj9cOcQSFjB9yDHwj.jpg', 'en', '/rNknh7XQUWvm4j9WeuhUJhT9NP4.jpg', 'On a special inner city street, the inhabitants—human and muppet—teach preschoolers basic educational and social concepts using comedy, cartoons, games, and songs.', 16, 55.294, 7.4, 'US', 102, 502),
('Sete Pecados', 'Sete Pecados', '2007-06-18', '/fCAuMDWBwjQZgPvnm1AuXUaD3qx.jpg', 'pt', '/vKa4SHat5AWGtq7EUasuaBfsxPi.jpg', 'Sete Pecados is a Brazilian telenovela airing at 7:00 pm, which replaced Pé na Jaca of Carlos Lombardi. The telenovela was written by Walcyr Carrasco, with the collaboration of Claudia Soto and Andre Ryoki. The directors were Jorge Fernando, Pedro Vasconcelos and Fred Mayrink. Jorge worked with the same directing cast on his previous telenovelas Chocolate com Pimenta and Alma Gêmea. Seven Sins debuted on June 18, 2007. and last aired on February 15, 2008, with 209 episodes.', 10766, 1.23, 0, 'BR', 0, 13979),
('Seth MacFarlane\'s Cavalcade of Cartoon Comedy', 'Seth MacFarlane\'s Cavalcade of Cartoon Comedy', '2008-09-10', '/yvrXcPtcQ0hC0h1UCsjvLonKYIk.jpg', 'en', '/nIc0tnEWxrQr1mEXOJHzhkhhsLG.jpg', 'Seth MacFarlane\'s Cavalcade of Cartoon Comedy is an American cartoon web series created by Seth MacFarlane. The series is based on the cutaway jokes on Family Guy.', 16, 6.924, 6.6, 'US', 11, 7985),
('Seven Days', 'Seven Days', '1998-10-07', '/A7wDQBnCejIcyeINg65OW17eJOL.jpg', 'en', '/oD7TudMCP51OZi97D55VsyOFslF.jpg', '\"Ever wish you could live your last week all over again? Well, my name\'s Frank B. Parker, and I do it all the time. I work for a secret government project experimenting in time travel. When things really get screwed up, I\'m the guinea pig they send back to take care of it. The catch is, I can only go back 7 days.\"', 18, 6.445, 7.3, 'US', 28, 4562),
('Seven Seconds', 'Seven Seconds', '2018-02-23', '/dhVMKKQ31LC7IxM374LCYexNyVT.jpg', 'en', '/mexUP20U3sPzu8jfGeRIHzI3TUC.jpg', 'Tensions run high between African American citizens and Caucasian cops in Jersey City when a teenage African American boy is critically injured by a cop.', 80, 6.081, 7.5, 'US', 34, 75540),
('Seven Worlds, One Planet', 'Seven Worlds, One Planet', '2019-10-27', '/qcz31McijELAjoEw6xZCrTjyIiN.jpg', 'en', '/kzKNMIlqyznC1jjht8mI2oEtDcp.jpg', 'Millions of years ago, incredible forces ripped apart the Earth’s crust creating seven extraordinary continents. This documentary series reveals how each distinct continent has shaped the unique animal life found there.', 99, 13.694, 9.1, 'GB', 10, 90790);
