('The Great Adventurer Wesley', 'The Great Adventurer Wesley', '2018-04-09', '/5u6jViw1qvd1yFvZ9fIhN6PLa5y.jpg', 'zh', '/wFLTofzqWqdsEnKtj6uRE1GsluB.jpg', '', 9648, 2.457, 8, 'CN', 1, 78756),
('The Great British Bake Off', 'The Great British Bake Off', '2010-08-17', '/nH97QreDeu6jnNKXIJQCaA91oDb.jpg', 'en', '/4lkXuLZhxUczr8ufy0tKgSRRYD2.jpg', 'This British television baking competition selects from amongst its competitors the best amateur baker. The series is credited with reinvigorating interest in baking throughout the UK, and many of its participants, including winners, have gone on to start a career based on baking.', 10764, 6.108, 7.7, 'GB', 43, 34549),
('The Great Indoors', 'The Great Indoors', '2016-10-27', '/9wRWk34jxdEMfByR2MLwYAcbDbf.jpg', 'en', '/7stveEz5wCtvuTXj3uAvoIvklEG.jpg', 'An adventure reporter must adapt to the times when he becomes the boss to a group of millennials in the digital department of the magazine.', 35, 6.891, 5.3, 'US', 34, 67157),
('The Greatest American Hero', 'The Greatest American Hero', '1981-03-18', '/4TOCKQJ8mt7DLlldAVeHb1NVm6O.jpg', 'en', '/8Npk9RVeAH1DA7kpommoUUWNAWy.jpg', 'The chronicles of  teacher Ralph Hinkley\'s adventures after a group of aliens gives him a red suit that gives him superhuman abilities. Unfortunately, Ralph, who hates wearing the suit, immediately loses its instruction booklet, and thus has to learn how to use its powers by trial and error, often with comical results.', 10759, 5.056, 7.2, 'US', 26, 1909),
