('The Tudors', 'The Tudors', '2007-04-01', '/zDY5fG4WpD1OwnVA0sIxGwGD0X5.jpg', 'en', '/96IFXF6eeMpFU1MDlXnaVtMBsaE.jpg', 'The Tudors is a history-based drama series following the young, vibrant King Henry VIII, a competitive and lustful monarch who navigates the intrigues of the English court and the human heart with equal vigor and justifiable suspicion.', 18, 14.56, 7.8, 'US', 181, 2942),
