('Twelve O\'Clock High', 'Twelve O\'Clock High', '1964-09-18', '/uVwpgONFTk730xrEieepqn5J4Jr.jpg', 'en', '/7OcdqXqw13fvUC7mjFFLyw239ix.jpg', 'This series chronicles the adventures--in the air and on the ground--of the men of the 918th Bombardment Group of the U.S. Eighth Air Force. First commanded by irascible General Frank Savage--and later by Colonel Joe Gallagher, the son of a Pentagon General--the Group is stationed in England, and flies long-range bombing missions into German-held Europe.', 18, 3.466, 8.4, 'US', 8, 13905),
