('Twin Peaks', 'Twin Peaks', '1990-04-08', '/1kt6k6upIgZQann2lqkZxfHNeLV.jpg', 'en', '/6W6zWBAay6XVBgJsOu6c2mlFZ8l.jpg', 'The body of Laura Palmer is washed up on a beach near the small Washington state town of Twin Peaks. FBI Special Agent Dale Cooper is called in to investigate her strange demise only to uncover a web of mystery that ultimately leads him deep into the heart of the surrounding woodland and his very own soul.', 18, 32.279, 8.2, 'US', 863, 1920),
('Twisted', 'Twisted', '2013-03-19', '/i66ljwkhiHNwxA7SoIWluAcBzef.jpg', 'en', '/gcz12mySnAnbO4I3k86P3NVY9Cv.jpg', 'A one-hour mystery full of twists and turns that follows Danny Desai, a charismatic 16-year-old with a troubled past who returns to his hometown after spending five years in juvenile detention. Immediately branded an outcast, Danny attempts to reconnect with his two childhood best friends, Jo and Lacey. But when a fellow student is found dead in her home, Danny instantly becomes the prime suspect and town spirals into a frenzy of suspicion and mystery. Jo and Lacey must decide if their childhood friend is unforgivable, or if he\'s really a victim being persecuted for his own twisted secrets.', 18, 5.438, 7.1, 'US', 26, 46661),
('Two and a Half Men', 'Two and a Half Men', '2003-09-21', '/27cshLy9anL9G0g6tBQjWkPACx5.jpg', 'en', '/A9QDK4OWpv41W27kCv0LXe30k9S.jpg', 'A hedonistic jingle writer\'s free-wheeling life comes to an abrupt halt when his brother and 10-year-old nephew move into his beach-front house.', 35, 100.022, 6.4, 'US', 813, 2691),
('Two Guys and a Girl', 'Two Guys and a Girl', '1998-03-10', '/5DuK5TET80dSu3SufdHMvsX0P6B.jpg', 'en', '/jFLDDn8XAOIv2sZ0aviiR7BSVbL.jpg', 'Two Guys and a Girl is an American sitcom', 35, 10.065, 7.3, 'US', 64, 75),
('Two Sentence Horror Stories', 'Two Sentence Horror Stories', '2019-08-08', '/qByqMVjNjGBTGMZJaYJQI7kbuAs.jpg', 'en', '/das40AqIwF9jQvqhyJMlH5aM8cN.jpg', 'An anthology series featuring updated tales of horror and haunting for the digital age, inspired by the viral fan fiction of two sentence horror stories.', 9648, 4.36, 5.4, 'US', 8, 90961),
('Tyler Perry\'s If Loving You Is Wrong', 'Tyler Perry\'s If Loving You Is Wrong', '2014-09-09', '/g3dl2WFxDNXUK2Qovli5iEqAlC1.jpg', 'en', '/wzYQGEYYvZyeuSWMHbQvhvOh8lc.jpg', 'Follow the relationships of a group of husbands and wives that live and love on the same street. While the neighbors come from very different backgrounds, their lives are similar – raising children, dealing with exes, worrying about money and keeping romance in their relationships. But just below the surface — secrets, lies and deception threaten to destroy what they have built.', 18, 8.685, 7.4, 'US', 42, 62251),
('Tyler Perry\'s Sistas', 'Tyler Perry\'s Sistas', '2019-10-23', '/8pWr7esugITmgrH22OXVmRg8xks.jpg', 'en', '/5MuT0LxU7iUA10GzKfH53o0p0kc.jpg', 'There\'s nothing that bonds a group of single black women together more than sidestepping the land mines of living, working and dating in Atlanta. In a sea of swipe-lefts, social media drama and unrealistic #relationshipgoals, these friends try to find their Mr. Right.', 35, 4.838, 7.7, 'US', 11, 94686),
('Tyler Perry\'s The Haves and the Have Nots', 'Tyler Perry\'s The Haves and the Have Nots', '2013-05-28', '/oXQL2ahBekJt3cfUpiXVUnNAQ11.jpg', 'en', '/bwQchLBTtu0lKLjmY7VJ7f3GfEi.jpg', 'Follow the complicated dynamic between the rich and powerful Cryer family and the hired help who work in their opulent Savannah, Georgia, mansion.', 18, 11.475, 7.5, 'US', 88, 46441),
('Tyler Perry\'s The Oval', 'Tyler Perry\'s The Oval', '2019-10-23', '/4fbTJ9AL9cls2qPV3CGE4fXK8Pl.jpg', 'en', '/hehSIBmty0uzFQUqhOW9S5zHtMh.jpg', 'A seemingly perfect interracial first family becomes the White House\'s newest residents. But behind closed doors they unleash a torrent of lies, cheating and corruption.', 18, 8.439, 9, 'US', 8, 95004),
('Typewriter', 'Typewriter', '2019-07-19', '/21bzCLmK3g7B27aojzxZWW9hFww.jpg', 'hi', '/evL7Es24fdV9Gwb3dUABzw7ViY0.jpg', 'Three young friends in Goa plan to search an old villa for ghosts, but when a new family, accompanied by their attractive daughter moves in, the home\'s buried past resurfaces in chilling ways and the amateur ghost hunters must spring into action.', 18, 5.402, 6.9, 'IN', 8, 91290),
('Tyrant', 'Tyrant', '2014-06-24', '/dzLo7Ka4uyKAT0rnSeSb5sAkSXD.jpg', 'en', '/kbEBxv8g4BMUQZ0ilObfSUv24Kl.jpg', 'The story of an unassuming American family drawn into the workings of a turbulent Middle Eastern nation. Bassam \"Barry\" Al Fayeed, the younger son of the dictator of a war-torn nation, ends a self-imposed 20-year exile to return to his homeland, accompanied by his American wife and children, for his nephew\'s wedding. Barry’s reluctant homecoming leads to a dramatic clash of cultures as he is thrown back into the familial and national politics of his youth.', 18, 9.535, 6.8, 'US', 91, 60972),
('Ufak Tefek Cinayetler', 'Stiletto Vendetta', '2017-10-24', '/ugvEdNmt1x4B4KHKRO8QdaOmaWr.jpg', 'tr', '/Askr1wn1bJIzihd1DiGoy1exZ54.jpg', 'Three girls in high school made a prank on the fourth girl and caused her to be expelled from the high school with her teacher. After 20 years they got together in a high society environment.', 18, 5.638, 7.1, 'TR', 4, 74660),
('UFO', 'UFO', '1970-09-16', '/1Z1au4GdiO2iRpPbBwtz8K1dCB4.jpg', 'en', '/zegZbrePgyYjL70xySD8kIl1Yev.jpg', 'A secret, high-technology international agency called SHADO defends Earth from alien invaders.', 10765, 6.871, 8.1, 'GB', 13, 2560),
('Ugly Americans', 'Ugly Americans', '2010-03-17', '/tMCSgfSMrVaJpmgbbnPWSHYVTkC.jpg', 'en', '/gFB8nca5PEvgM7HbWIzrkcNJTxO.jpg', 'Ugly Americans is an American animated sitcom created by Devin Clark and developed by David M. Stern. The program focuses on the life of Mark Lilly, a social worker employed by the Department of Integration, in an alternate reality version of New York City inhabited by monsters and other creatures. Daniel Powell serves as executive producer and Aaron Augenblick is supervising producer and animation director.\n\nUgly Americans aired on Comedy Central from March 17, 2010 to April 25, 2012 with a total of 31 episodes over two seasons.', 16, 4.05, 7, 'US', 49, 32351);
INSERT INTO `series` (`Name`, `Original_name`, `First_air_date`, `Backdrop_path`, `Original_language`, `Poster_path`, `Overview`, `Genre_ids`, `Popularity`, `Vote_average`, `Origin_country`, `Vote_count`, `id`) VALUES
('Ugly Betty', 'Ugly Betty', '2006-09-28', '/3NoDPgGQi6afTxpoOWgIly3oGs9.jpg', 'en', '/5W64XnpFAId4gGyRrR6nmafE8lV.jpg', 'Smart but wholesome Betty embraces her unique appearance and independent attitude in the cutthroat world of New York fashion. With the help of her proud yet far-from-glamorous family from Queens, Betty will continue to have big dreams and deal with any obstacle in her own unique style.', 35, 9.124, 5.7, 'US', 100, 4626),
('Ultraman', 'Ultraman', '2019-04-01', '/vgoeMt2R5DdwK7DCbJJUS2Vkah7.jpg', 'ja', '/yt3jAozd4EmWsUyhKAY3viStAO6.jpg', 'Decades ago, a hero from the stars left this world in peace. Now, the son of Ultraman must rise to protect the Earth from a new alien threat.', 16, 6.898, 7.4, 'JP', 9, 80795),
('Um Himmels Willen', 'For Heaven\'s Sake', '2002-01-08', '/1KuOouZfoSuTpHIJeeRiZLyEpVg.jpg', 'de', '/t6l2AbhLOjIDvfqSwvqJpcMchJX.jpg', 'Sister Hanna is a spirited, witty, resolute, warm-hearted, and - attractive nun. With her wit and street cred, she takes charge of Kaltenthal Cloister, transforming it into a popular refuge for all those seeking help of one kind or another. She also brings new life to the sleepy provincial community, proving herself quite a match for her great rival and opponent, the mayor Wolfgang Wöller.', 35, 6.93, 0, 'DE', 0, 40891),
('Umbre', 'Shadows', '2014-12-28', '/AsJLJOlkx3IbVgehgGpfSOwyGKW.jpg', 'ro', '/xe5llTidI6HUPFAmgtLgGig1JbS.jpg', 'Relu is a family man. He has two children, a wife and a double life. Seen through the eyes of his family, Relu Oncescu appears to be an ordinary taxi driver. No one suspects that Relu works as a collector for Capitanu\', a local mobster. Neither of the two worlds (his family and the mafia) knows of the other\'s existence. Relu manages to keep everything under control, but not for long. After accidentally killing a man, he tries to get out of the underworld, but he can\'t find his way back. Day by day, the secrets he keeps become increasingly oppressive and the lies begin to surface, one by one.', 80, 5.976, 8.8, 'RO', 13, 62111),
('Un Bore Mercher', 'Keeping  Faith', '2017-11-05', '/4PrbHZ3XNWedhKNSSi4Nwb9L5By.jpg', 'cy', '/loZ2f0rbBwwnGXr6lSaOA4dGPV3.jpg', 'Faith, a small-town Welsh lawyer, is forced to cut short her extended maternity leave when her husband and business partner, Evan, goes missing.  As the truth of his actions surface, Faith must fight to protect her family and her sanity.', 18, 4.138, 6.1, 'GB', 8, 75592),
('Un Camino Hacia el Destino', 'Road to Destiny', '2016-01-25', '/eNJrGOG3EM3k0IkdDnLbCi9cOmg.jpg', 'es', '/6ZWY5SdZP8XE9WemJYogg9hMsLN.jpg', 'Luisa Fernanda Pérez, a beautiful, 18-year-old student, has two passions: mastering the violin and gardening, a skill she learned from her father, Pedro, the former groundskeeper of the wealthy Altamirano family’s estate. A chance encounter with destiny alters her life after she is injured in a car accident caused by Luis (her biological father), a playboy lawyer and falls for his stepson, Carlos, an attractive, young doctor treating her at the local hospital.', 18, 2.804, 3.8, 'MX', 3, 66886),
('Un medico in famiglia', 'Un medico in famiglia', '1998-12-06', '/z1vhAKz2ww9DnLSDJdbjIJfFpS1.jpg', 'it', '/qH1jh5SAvs0LtmWPZMRjTPWl9i.jpg', 'Un medico in famiglia is an Italian television TV series. The show is inspired, to an extent, by Spanish TV series Médico de familia. It is one of the most successful series in Italy.', 35, 1.973, 0, 'IT', 0, 31390),
('Un paso adelante', 'Un paso adelante', '2002-01-08', '/yszqDZBbxQvpT6mwneB8W3ah1p.jpg', 'es', '/jGqlQm5ujR1dTfZqgjvBe1lCMYc.jpg', 'Un Paso Adelante was a Spanish TV drama similar to the American 1980’s TV series Fame. It was originally broadcast on Spanish channel Antena 3 from 2002 to 2005. It has also been a huge success in Spanish-speaking countries, in Germany, Italy, Serbia, Montenegro and in France. It began airing on Séries+ in Canada in 2011.', 18, 4.675, 3.5, 'ES', 4, 6798),
('Un Rostro en mi Pasado', 'Un Rostro en mi Pasado', '1989-10-16', '/1I8UbUDNaE6FVbwrpZLcfkQobN2.jpg', 'es', '/wzAHqSd4LmlCWGNXjufusGWQSPY.jpg', '', 18, 1.216, 0, 'MX', 0, 87311),
('Un si grand soleil', 'Chronicles of the Sun', '2018-08-27', '/aizbHLcKVWvJ7jxkflJzTu5Z8GE.jpg', 'fr', '/t6jVlbPMtZOJoAOfeoR4yQmnjXM.jpg', '', 0, 1.326, 0, 'FR', 0, 81329),
('Unbelievable', 'Unbelievable', '2019-09-13', '/yG5oWkFH8xle6xkD2JB7HWfuSGx.jpg', 'en', '/jHOrNJNM03Lsjdw7nsw7TlqBOhd.jpg', 'A teenager is charged with lying about her rape allegation, but two determined investigative female detectives discover a far more sinister truth.', 18, 13.93, 8.2, 'US', 57, 91275),
('Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt', 'Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt', '2015-03-06', '/dG25UWq95YSIxovAjALLQwsg1x2.jpg', 'en', '/5rj9fHmVA1r54wjCpPw5ScW0WT2.jpg', 'When a woman is rescued from a doomsday cult and lands in New York City, she must navigate a world she didn’t think even existed anymore.', 35, 13.968, 7.3, 'US', 228, 61671),
('Uncle Grandpa', 'Uncle Grandpa', '2013-09-02', '/tsa0c2Ce7WsMFE8ABW2vD9U7Str.jpg', 'en', '/efoe6sQw3nWc2hPWKB3qC0s7O7q.jpg', 'The adventures of Uncle Grandpa who is out to help every child and adult in the world through the power of imagination. With his mystical R.V. and eternal optimism, Uncle Grandpa is always ready to greet the day - and everyone he meets - with his signature, \"Good Mornin\'.\"', 16, 4.86, 3.6, 'US', 30, 47035),
('Undateable', 'Undateable', '2014-05-29', '/ubIgLoGyOIZqZ1HekOtSzU1iBo7.jpg', 'en', '/2gzAHXMdkTAZjRA1Hf8th3rT2sJ.jpg', 'Whether it\'s due to a lack of style, the wrong job, or even just a bad haircut, everyone goes through a time in their lives when they\'re undateable. Most of us eventually grow out of it, but some people need a little more help than others. Enter Danny Burton. Confident, attractive and impervious to outside opinions, 29-year-old Danny – who may be in a state of arrested development himself – decides to help out his new roommate, Justin Kearney, the owner of an unsuccessful bar and a chronic overthinker, and Justin\'s group of oddball friends – Shelly, Burski and Brett. Danny introduces the gang to his recently divorced older sister, Leslie, who immediately bonds with this group of guys, as she feels a little stuck in her own life as well. The gang spends most of their time at Justin\'s bar, helping solve each other\'s respective problems over beers, and while they love to give each other a hard time, they always have each other\'s back.\n\nPlot Summary:\n\nDanny Burton is a 30-ish carefree single guy who has watched most of his friends move on to serious relationships. When his last remaining friend Shannon moves out to get married, Danny searches for a new roommate. A promising candidate is Justin, the owner of Black Eyes Bar in Detroit (frequently mispronounced \"Black Guys Bar\"). Justin and his friends - the nerdy Burski, oddball Shelly, and recently out-of-the-closet gay guy Brett - all have certain qualities that make them appear \"undateable\". While Danny himself has good luck getting women into bed, he is unable or unwilling to form a lasting commitment with any of them. Danny\'s attractive sister, Leslie, has similar fears about being undateable, having the \"baggage\" of being a mid-30s divorcee.', 35, 5.564, 6.5, 'US', 34, 51345),
('Undeclared', 'Undeclared', '2001-09-25', '/5rWNng2pNitZ73BH8uSFW9YrdyQ.jpg', 'en', '/ke9YSQ8SC4xupmBAX9tLMAZ635j.jpg', 'College freshman Steve Karp, his girlfriend and their fellow dorm-mates embark on one the greatest experiences of their lives...unfortunately for Steve, his lonely and recently divorced father is tagging along for the ride.', 35, 4.197, 7.4, 'US', 54, 3948),
('Under the Dome', 'Under the Dome', '2013-06-24', '/cJotBRRn7zj4Ed95ibusfU4pqis.jpg', 'en', '/iFnCH70twxNDICQlDuCcoEt4Jma.jpg', 'A small town is suddenly and inexplicably sealed off from the rest of the world by an enormous transparent dome. While military forces, the government and the media positioned outside of this surrounding barrier attempt to break it down, a small group of people inside attempt to figure out what the dome is, where it came from, and when (and if) it will go away.', 18, 14.791, 6.3, 'US', 525, 46331),
('Underbelly', 'Underbelly', '2008-02-13', '/5MesRhWQeaNMuWeSjJRDOr4GNZH.jpg', 'en', '/hgXETmrV2Jc1LrqtwJePLWW0DE6.jpg', 'Underbelly is an Australian television true crime-drama series which broadcasts on the Nine Network. Each series is based on real-life events.', 18, 6.826, 7.3, 'AU', 16, 13796),
('Undercover', 'Undercover', '2019-02-24', '/gwNXpQxRX0YYsr2HPfrSoxmZc05.jpg', 'nl', '/vxMMFnDCMw9ZCSHNQSb2XLNr7gt.jpg', 'Undercover agents infiltrate a drug kingpin\'s operation by posing as a couple at the campground where he spends his weekends. Inspired by real events.', 80, 3.901, 8, 'BE', 14, 86942),
('Undercover Boss', 'Undercover Boss', '2010-02-07', '/pAmXh91RM2vwQF1C4IZdYZiDnPx.jpg', 'en', '/tyydTLz1HFiMWdTXoQxclJJpsUz.jpg', 'Reality series that follows high-level executives as they slip anonymously into the rank-and-file of their own organizations. Each week, a different leader will sacrifice the comfort of their corner office for an undercover mission to examine the inner workings of their operation.', 99, 7.54, 5.2, 'US', 25, 33297),
('Underdog', 'Underdog', '1964-10-03', '/4yZL5svaBEii4w7aw5VzLqEKmxQ.jpg', 'en', '/lfB9P9BLJ4GbjzzQ0IgEC0CVXDt.jpg', 'Underdog is an American animated television series that debuted October 3, 1964, on the NBC network under the primary sponsorship of General Mills, and continued in syndication until 1973, for a run of 124 episodes.\n\nUnderdog, Shoeshine Boy\'s heroic alter-ego, appeared whenever love interest Sweet Polly Purebred was being victimized by such villains as Simon Bar Sinister or Riff Raff. Underdog nearly always speaks in rhyme, as in, \"There\'s no need to fear, Underdog is here!\" His voice was supplied by Wally Cox.', 16, 8.233, 7, 'US', 12, 4979),
('Underground', 'Underground', '2016-03-09', '/4r0HvYsmDes4vW98CWJvRDengk5.jpg', 'en', '/yagYxDeC0Ru36U1CPLC3mn0B8O.jpg', 'A group of slaves plan a daring 600-mile escape from a Georgia plantation. Along the way, they are aided by a secret abolitionist couple running a station on the Underground Railroad as they attempt to evade the people charged with bringing them back, dead or alive.', 18, 4.96, 6.8, 'US', 56, 64150),
('Undone', 'Undone', '2019-09-13', '/4HPRLBGgG0hUZXE0HA98vuWxPCt.jpg', 'en', '/wwCclQaT9tIAHVbAkGwQvnNUSm6.jpg', 'After getting into a near fatal car accident, Alma discovers she has a new relationship with time and uses this ability to find out the truth about her father’s death.', 16, 12.722, 7.9, 'US', 35, 86340),
('Une île', 'The Woman from the Sea', '2020-01-09', '/200ESPuCH0MhBlyDS2kpcqtTrGD.jpg', 'fr', '/btMVKcFNZKYIJZhfcCyeRoqVOLE.jpg', '', 80, 5.371, 5, 'FR', 2, 87780),
('Unfabulous', 'Unfabulous', '2004-09-12', '/64DoFNkKUu1YsJBvSB668FhJaB4.jpg', 'en', '/guOmfdUPV8wDqpNqA9rsfzuq6Sx.jpg', 'Unfabulous is an American children\'s television series that aired on Nickelodeon. The series is about an \"unfabulous\" 7th Grade middle school student named Addie Singer, played by Emma Roberts. The show, which debuted in late summer 2004, was one of the most-watched programs in the United States among children between the age of 10 and 16 and was created by Sue Rose, who previously created the animated series Pepper Ann and Angela Anaconda.\n\nThe series ended on December 16, 2007, with the third season being the last.\n\nReruns of the show ended on Nickelodeon on June 2008. The show aired reruns on The N but ended in late 2009. The show then returned to TeenNick on October 11, 2011, and lasted until April 2, 2012. The show returned to the channel again on December 3, 2012.\n\nAll the episodes are narrated by Addie, and are told in flashbacks. The episode titles all start with the article \"The\".\n\nThe show\'s theme song is performed by Jill Sobule, who also writes the songs for the series.', 35, 3.201, 7.9, 'US', 11, 2967),
('Unforgettable', 'Unforgettable', '2011-09-20', '/w65WBmhPROXkFYcU79zGsKJ1HqP.jpg', 'en', '/m2xnZgn4eau3e2d84mWD2h0JtRL.jpg', 'Former Syracuse, New York, police detective Carrie Wells has hyperthymesia, a rare medical condition that gives her the ability to visually remember everything. She reluctantly joins the New York City Police Department\'s Queens homicide unit after her former boyfriend and partner asks for help with solving a case. The move allows her to try to find out the one thing she has been unable to remember, which is what happened the day her sister was murdered.', 80, 9.68, 6.4, 'US', 101, 39276),
('Unforgotten', 'Unforgotten', '2015-10-08', '/kXkt4SQHnpX0EpvbtWrRCrG5B6.jpg', 'en', '/93xoQvdgZCmPx4GHorgz2ibA4P9.jpg', '\'Unforgotten\' follows modern police team DCI Cassie Stuart and DI Sunny Khan, who gradually unravel long-forgotten secrets which have a dramatic impact on their investigation and the four potential suspects. The slow revelation of the secrets will also affect the personal lives of both Sunny and Cassie.', 18, 5.627, 7.8, 'GB', 51, 62505),
('Unhappily Ever After', 'Unhappily Ever After', '1995-01-11', '/lC7qEuT2V3Ko8HhEDNDATyF0VtU.jpg', 'en', '/zr4SMxpXf6UtKxlJshBuqNMRBhF.jpg', 'Unhappily Ever After is an American sitcom that aired for 100 episodes on The WB network from January 11, 1995, to May 23, 1999, for a total of five seasons. The series was produced by Touchstone Television.', 35, 3.75, 6.7, 'US', 8, 6515),
('UNHhhh', 'UNHhhh', '2016-03-25', '/yhsQvMJSYAku5AgHTuTXrNHx16r.jpg', 'en', '/A69k4Ef1gvtoGWA6s8COBJYn45q.jpg', 'RuPaul\'s Drag Race season 7 queens Katya Zamolodchikova and Trixie Mattel in \'UNHhhh.\' It\'s a show about nothing, and yet it\'s about everything.', 35, 4.967, 9.3, 'US', 3, 75127),
('Unité 42', 'Unit 42', '2017-11-19', '/nWxWBNe3oGs5XxVIjXfIIfjE5Sm.jpg', 'fr', '/k6c81W7DFuKdSx5jtfUj7X8Z6NV.jpg', 'The investigations of two police officers from The Brussels Digital Unit, a unit specializing in cybercrime.', 80, 4.843, 6, 'BE', 12, 72429),
('Unité 9', 'Unite 9', '2012-09-11', '/mGZvpmjgAd0rI8c7TvdeQch4gib.jpg', 'fr', '/a7BSR0gOji04GNl0avydat3Y1ju.jpg', 'Marie Lamontagne, a widowed mother of two in her forties, confesses to a murder she didn\'t commit to protect her daughter. Thrust into brutally unfamiliar and hostile surroundings, she first learns survival, then confronts the biggest challenge of her life: bonding with her fellow inmates and helping them take back control of their lives.', 18, 4.422, 5.8, 'CA', 4, 61306),
('United States of Tara', 'United States of Tara', '2009-01-18', '/yVXsaYt6eJtiSSGnHfanuMffViO.jpg', 'en', '/1In2RKtViEKkWKd4ECcTY8lCup4.jpg', 'Tara\'s multiple personalities include \"T\" the wild-child teenager, \"Buck\" the rough and tumble biker dude, and \"Alice\" the type-A homemaker. But with a family that loves her just the way she is, Tara never gives up hope that someday she can just be herself.', 35, 7.181, 7.1, 'US', 69, 7097),
('University Challenge', 'University Challenge', '1962-09-21', '/sOSWYhlxMJ7mmAOR4e2UrnJjNtd.jpg', 'en', '/ydj0UDj0DPaSvN01JWOJjYkrnEV.jpg', 'Academic quiz show where teams of students from UK universities answer questions on all manner of subjects.', 0, 3.304, 5.3, 'GB', 3, 5266),
('UnREAL', 'UnREAL', '2015-06-01', '/b6BMG4g2eiP3IJMN7utVpHk7p1Y.jpg', 'en', '/tNnGxtP1b8zy2x64z9AvYDpwpwZ.jpg', 'Set against the backdrop of a hit dating competition show, \"UnREAL\" is led by Rachel, a young staffer whose sole job is to manipulate her relationships with and among the contestants to get the vital dramatic and outrageous footage the program\'s dispassionate executive producer demands. What ensues is a humorous, yet vexing, look at what happens in the world of unscripted television, where being a contestant can be vicious and producing it is a whole other reality.', 18, 9.648, 6.4, 'US', 78, 62335),
('Unser Charly', 'Unser Charly', '1995-12-27', '/cOEcqK37uyziwjtCHfKHrXyivYt.jpg', 'de', '/mrRBzJqvKR6xCNXmHEiiXBhUSf.jpg', 'Unser Charly is a German television series.', 35, 3.688, 0, 'DE', 0, 23325),
('Unsere Mütter, unsere Väter', 'Generation War', '2013-03-17', '/eVhtztlR0qe1XgEkVpTQUqol9oi.jpg', 'de', '/lQKe2rx4tx5rxLbQhFb2fQAXRBw.jpg', 'Berlin, summer of 1941, during the World War II. Five young Germans promise to meet again as soon the war ends… in Christmas: brothers Wilhelm and Friedhelm will go to the Russian front. Charlotte will serve as a nurse in a campaign hospital. Greta dreams of becoming a singer. Viktor, her Jewish boyfriend, works as a tailor with her father. But soon their naive wishes of peace and happiness will become a long and tragic nightmare.', 18, 7.194, 8.2, 'DE', 156, 46849),
('Unsolved Mysteries', 'Unsolved Mysteries', '1987-01-20', '/z9PAC1fKtcKCERAvB8Edvy2AG2X.jpg', 'en', '/9KDXxWsc76QpUQiW9HlReFHgHg9.jpg', 'Unsolved Mysteries is an American television program, hosted by Robert Stack from 1987 until 2002 and later by Dennis Farina starting in 2008. In addition, TV presenter Keely Shaye Smith and actress Virginia Madsen contributed greatly to its success. Keely Shaye played the role of a reporter from the confines of an office interacting with Stack and responding to questions for further information. In this capacity, she was a welcomed addition to the cast and revered tremendously by Stack, who would \"cut to\" her for more detailed information. Academy-award-winning actress Virginia Madsen\'s contribution to the show included performing in Stack\'s role as announcer for several years. It was broadcast first as specials in 1987, then as a regular series on NBC, CBS, Lifetime and Spike. Lifetime once again airs the revived version of the series, but only in reruns.\n\nAlthough the show is not in current production, Cosgrove-Meurer Productions maintains a website for the show, featuring popular accounts and still unsolved crimes, with a link to an online form should a viewer have information on an unsolved crime.', 9648, 4.26, 7.9, 'US', 27, 126),
