('What\'s Happening!!', 'What\'s Happening!!', '1976-08-05', '/lZjYIXWWHtRno2m8IgD4oTeBgET.jpg', 'en', '/oaDvj8di0QjPuxqnANxT9ybn0E1.jpg', 'What\'s Happening!! is an American television sitcom that aired on ABC from August 5, 1976 to April 28, 1979. The show premiered as a summer series. With good ratings and reviews, and after the failure of several other shows on the network, What\'s Happening!! returned in November 1976 as a weekly series. It remained a regular show until 1979; ratings were modest. What\'s Happening!! was loosely based on the motion picture Cooley High, also written by Eric Monte.', 35, 3.914, 8.3, 'US', 9, 1869),
